{"api_version": "2022-08-31", "model_id": "bc2-narrative", "content": "original narrative\nTITLE: AGGRAVATED MENACING/ETHNIC INTIMIDATION/NAMED SUSPECT\nOn 9/12/17 while assigned to Zone Car 3A22 we received a radio broadcast to the above address for neighbor dispute. Upon our arrival, we conferred with Reporting Person (Raya Robinson). Raya stated that her neighbor\u2019s friend, Offender/Louvenia Merlonghi yelled racial slurs at her daughter, Victim/Arieon Hickman. Raya and the neighbor across the street have been having ongoing issues. As we conferred with Arieon she stated that Louvenia yelled at her saying, \u201cTell your momI kill kids too\u201d and \u201cI\u2019ll blowall your nigger heads off\u201d as she was playing in the street.\nConferred with 3S23, Sgt. Gomez #9135 on scene and advised her of the Ethnic Intimidation. CCS advised ofEthnic Intimidation.\nRaya was given the Third District Detective Bureau phone number. Respectfully request Third District Detective Bureau to follow up. WCS in use.\nReport 17-296809 typed by D. Banks-Gates.\nYou created this PDF from an application that is not licensed to print to novaPDF printer (http://www.novapdf.com)\nPage: 7 of 7", "languages": [], "pages": [{"page_number": 7, "angle": null, "width": 8.5, "height": 11.0, "unit": "inch", "lines": [{"content": "original narrative", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3318, "y": 0.3915}, {"x": 1.7643, "y": 0.3915}, {"x": 1.7643, "y": 0.5661}, {"x": 0.3318, "y": 0.5661}], "spans": [{"offset": 0, "length": 18}]}, {"content": "TITLE: AGGRAVATED MENACING/ETHNIC INTIMIDATION/NAMED SUSPECT", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3335, "y": 1.0321}, {"x": 5.4738, "y": 1.0321}, {"x": 5.4738, "y": 1.1323}, {"x": 0.3335, "y": 1.1323}], "spans": [{"offset": 19, "length": 60}]}, {"content": "On 9/12/17 while assigned to Zone Car 3A22 we received a radio broadcast to the above address for neighbor dispute.", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3666, "y": 1.3447}, {"x": 7.1743, "y": 1.3447}, {"x": 7.1743, "y": 1.4725}, {"x": 0.3666, "